{"type":"question","id":10445,"title":"如何評價這些不要民的成語？","uid":7699,"topics":[339,922],"contents":"[<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/publish/javascript:void(0)\">翠竹黄花</a>]　指眼前境物。<br>\n[<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/publish/javascript:void(0)\">翠消红减</a>]　形容女子姿容减退。<br>\n[<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/publish/javascript:void(0)\">翠围珠绕</a>]　翠：翡翠；珠：珍珠。形容富家女子的华丽装饰。亦比喻随从侍女众多。<br>\n[<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/publish/javascript:void(0)\">翠绕珠围</a>]　珠：珍珠；翠：翡翠。形容妇女妆饰华丽。也形容富贵人家随侍的女子众多。<br>\n[<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/publish/javascript:void(0)\">珠翠之珍</a>]　指水陆所产的美味食物。<br>\n[<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/publish/javascript:void(0)\">暮翠朝红</a>]　形容爱情不专一。<br>\n[<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/publish/javascript:void(0)\">刻翠裁红</a>]　比喻极力修饰词藻。<br>\n[<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/publish/javascript:void(0)\">浮翠流丹</a>]　翠：青绿色。丹：朱红色。青绿、朱红的颜色在流动和浮现。形容色彩鲜明艳丽。<br>\n[<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/publish/javascript:void(0)\">苍翠欲滴</a>]　苍翠：深绿。形容草木等绿色植物仿佛饱含水份一样。<br>\n[<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/publish/javascript:void(0)\">珠围翠拥</a>]　指华贵的装璜或装饰。<br>\n[<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/publish/javascript:void(0)\">珠围翠绕</a>]　珠：珍珠；翠：翡翠。形容妇女妆饰华丽。也形容富贵人家随侍的女子众多。<br>\n[<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/publish/javascript:void(0)\">珠歌翠舞</a>]　指声色美妙的歌舞。<br>\n[<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/publish/javascript:void(0)\">朱颜翠发</a>]　指青春年少。同“朱颜绿发”。<br>\n[<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/publish/javascript:void(0)\">红衰翠减</a>]　红：指花；翠：指绿叶。红花衰败，绿叶减少。形容春尽花残或初秋百花凋谢的景象。<br>\n[<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/publish/javascript:void(0)\">红飞翠舞</a>]　红、翠：指服装的色彩，泛指各种各样的颜色。形容妇女们穿着各种颜色的漂亮衣服，尽兴嬉戏，热闹非凡的情景。<br>\n[<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/publish/javascript:void(0)\">苍松翠柏</a>]　苍：青色。翠：青绿色。指四季常青的松柏。比喻具有高贵品质、坚定节操的人。<br>\n[<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/publish/javascript:void(0)\">偎红倚翠</a>]　指亲狎女色；狎妓。<br>\n[<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/publish/javascript:void(0)\">披罗戴翠</a>]　形容衣饰华丽。<br>\n[<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/publish/javascript:void(0)\">镂金铺翠</a>]　形容缤纷的色彩。<br>\n[<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/publish/javascript:void(0)\">眷红偎翠</a>]　形容对春色的依恋。<br>\n[<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/publish/javascript:void(0)\">裁红点翠</a>]　①采摘花卉。②比喻选择华丽的辞藻。","date":"2020-06-30","agreeCount":2,"discussionCount":0}